---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="CRM & Dashboard for Small Business — LeadFair"
  description="LeadFair's built-in CRM gives you a lead pipeline, call history, customizable dashboard, activity feed, and needs-attention alerts — all powered by AI. No more juggling five different apps."
  headline="Your Whole Business, One Screen"
  subheadline="LeadFair isn't just AI tools — it's a full CRM and command center. Every lead, every call, every follow-up, all in one place. No spreadsheets, no switching between apps."
  accentColor="primary"
>
  <!-- What's Inside -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dots opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-4">Everything You Need to Manage Your Business</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 text-lg">Most small businesses run on a patchwork of tools that don't talk to each other. LeadFair puts it all in one place.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Lead Pipeline</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Track every lead from first contact to closed deal. Search, filter, and move leads through custom stages. See where every opportunity stands at a glance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Call History & Summaries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Every call the AI receptionist handles is logged with a full summary — who called, what was discussed, and what action was taken. Search by date, caller, or status.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Customizable Dashboard</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Choose which widgets you see — call stats, leads needing attention, recent activity, repeat callers, calls by day, and more. Every owner's dashboard is different because every business is different.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Needs Attention Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">LeadFair flags what needs your attention — leads going cold, missed calls that need callbacks, automations that need review. Nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Activity Feed</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">A real-time stream of everything happening in your business — new leads, calls answered, automations fired, follow-ups sent. Open the dashboard and instantly know what's going on.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Auto-Sync from Calls</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">When the AI receptionist takes a call from a new person, it automatically creates a lead in your pipeline with the caller's info and a summary. No manual data entry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Scheduling Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Appointments booked by the AI receptionist flow straight into your dashboard. See upcoming bookings, manage availability, and track no-shows — all in one place.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It's Different -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-blue-green">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">How LeadFair's CRM Is Different</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">It's Connected to the AI</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Traditional CRMs store data. LeadFair's CRM is powered by the Company Companion — the same AI that answers your calls and runs your automations. When a lead calls, the AI already knows their history. When you ask the Companion about a lead, it pulls up everything instantly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">It Fills Itself In</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Most CRMs are empty until you spend hours entering data. LeadFair populates itself — every call the AI takes creates a lead, every follow-up gets logged, every status change is tracked automatically. You manage by exception, not by data entry.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">It's Simple on Purpose</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">No 50-tab setup wizard. No features you'll never use. LeadFair's CRM does what small businesses actually need — track leads, see calls, know what needs attention — without the complexity of tools built for enterprise sales teams.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-warm">
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Businesses tracking leads in spreadsheets or sticky notes</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Owners who want to see their whole business at a glance</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Anyone tired of entering the same info into three different apps</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Teams that tried HubSpot or Salesforce and found it way too much</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
